                "invention-title": [
                    "Integrated reaction device for producing methane through carbon dioxide trapping and hydrogenation",
                    "一种二氧化碳捕集加氢制甲烷一体化反应装置"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention belongs to the field of carbon dioxide resource utilization, and discloses a carbon dioxide capture and hydrogenation methane preparation integrated reaction device, which comprises an absorption tower, a desorption and hydrogenation integrated tower and a hydrogenation reaction tower, the absorbent absorbing carbon dioxide in the absorption tower passes through the heat exchanger, is desorbed in the desorption and hydrogenation integrated tower and then enters the gas-liquid separator; liquid separated by the gas-liquid separator exchanges heat with an absorbent which absorbs carbon dioxide and flows out of the absorption tower through a heat exchanger, and then enters the absorption tower again for carbon dioxide absorption; gas separated from the gas-liquid separator is mixed with hydrogen and then enters a desorption and hydrogenation integrated tower and a hydrogenation reaction tower; and a gas inlet of the hydrogenation reaction tower is connected with a pressure regulating valve. The device disclosed by the invention has the advantages of high systematization degree and low energy consumption."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明属于二氧化碳资源化利用领域，公开了一种二氧化碳捕集加氢制甲烷一体化反应装置，包括吸收塔、解吸加氢一体塔和加氢反应塔；所述的吸收塔内的吸收了二氧化碳的吸收剂经换热器后在所述的解吸加氢一体塔内解吸后进入气液分离器；经气液分离器分离后的液体经换热器与所述的吸收塔内流出的吸收了二氧化碳的吸收剂进行换热后重新进入到吸收塔内进行二氧化碳吸收；气液分离器中分离出的气体与氢气混合后进入解吸加氢一体塔和加氢反应塔；所述的加氢反应塔的进气口连接有调压阀。本发明的装置具有系统化程度高和能耗低的优点。"
                }
            ]
